        <Parent_String>West Turkestani historic textile styles [300244556], West Turkestani historic styles [300244838], West Turkestani historic styles and periods [300244553], West Turkestani [300244546], Central Asian [300018281], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
